": "", "timestamp": "Monday, October 27, 2025 2:38 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-27 2:38 p.m.", "text": "and how to measure? I have uptime, and total airtime TX and RX ..", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>and how to measure? I have uptime, and total airtime TX and RX ..</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1432438958922399836", "author": "recrof", "author_handle": "recrof", "user_id": "205303085910720514", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/205303085910720514/8ccde84f87c6a23fe1212f4c9a64a4b8.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Monday, October 27, 2025 2:41 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-27 2:41 p.m.", "text": "I guess only way to easily measure utilisation is by feeding it to HA or similar", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I guess only way to easily measure utilisation is by feeding it to HA or similar</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=thumbsup><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=👍 src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f44d.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1432457463549923389", "author": "🦦 Hilton Travis SMBI", "author_handle": "hiltontravissmbi", "user_id": "1430489846090043482", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1430489846090043482/d40eb19b82a2cb5fc68c6c0bc7093cc7.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Monday, October 27, 2025 3:54 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-27 3:54 p.m.", "text": "I have 2x Seeeeeed P1 Pro nodes that I'm testing and about to find better locations for, and 2x D5 Solar nodes in waiting for screen less T114 boards to arrive so I can replace the V3 boards (which will find other users).", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I have 2x Seeeeeed P1 Pro nodes that I&#39;m testing and about to find better locations for, and 2x D5 Solar nodes in waiting for screen less T114 boards to arrive so I can replace the V3 boards (which will find other users).</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "<div class=chatlog__reactions><div class=chatlog__reaction title=heart><img class=\"chatlog__emoji chatlog__emoji--small\" alt=❤️ src=https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/2764.svg loading=lazy> <span class=chatlog__reaction-count>1</span></div></div>", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1432465312036683878", "author": "Ceres Station 🌑", "author_handle": "82a6_31995", "user_id": "1416146698115485798", "avatar": "", "timestamp": "Monday, October 27, 2025 4:25 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-27 4:25 p.m.", "text": "measured with HA?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>measured with HA?</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "<div class=chatlog__reply><img class=chatlog__reply-avatar src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/135910101667020800/baa8599ffcf0bbbdcdee344b8397051c.png?size=512\" alt=Avatar loading=lazy><div class=chatlog__reply-author style=color:rgb(31,139,76) title=cisien>Cisien</div><div class=chatlog__reply-content><span class=chatlog__reply-link onclick=\"scrollToMessage(event,'1432463722688811140')\"> currently at 10-15% </span></div></div>", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1432469417887006822", "author": "Ceres Station 🌑", "author_handle": "82a6_31995", "user_id": "1416146698115485798", "avatar": "", "timestamp": "Monday, October 27, 2025 4:42 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-27 4:42 p.m.", "text": "awesome. that's what i was thinking, just wanted to confirm what other folks are doing. also belatedly realizing this post isn't really about solar", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>awesome. that&#39;s what i was thinking, just wanted to confirm what other folks are doing. also belatedly realizing this post isn&#39;t really about solar <img\n    loading=\"lazy\"\n    class=\"chatlog__emoji \"\n    alt=\"😄\"\n    title=\"smile\"\n    src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/twitter/twemoji@latest/assets/svg/1f604.svg\"></span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1432469800394821693", "author": "🦦 Hilton Travis SMBI", "author_handle": "hiltontravissmbi", "user_id": "1430489846090043482", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1430489846090043482/d40eb19b82a2cb5fc68c6c0bc7093cc7.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Monday, October 27, 2025 4:43 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-27 4:43 p.m.", "text": "I'm looking at options to build reliable solar nodes instead of buying pre-built. The one big issue with the D5 chassis is it's mounting as compared the Seeeeeed P1 - the D5 has a flimsy plastic screw-mount and one connecting point whereas the P1 has a beefy pole-mount with two connecting points into the chassis. The P1 mount can also be screw-mounted to a wall. The other issue with the D5 is the inclusion of a Heltec V3 with a screen, instead of a screen less T114 (or other bfr hardware). So, considering options here... (edited)", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>I&#39;m looking at options to build reliable solar nodes instead of buying pre-built.  The one big issue with the D5 chassis is it&#39;s mounting as compared the Seeeeeed P1 - the D5 has a flimsy plastic screw-mount and one connecting point whereas the P1 has a beefy pole-mount with two connecting points into the chassis.  The P1 mount can also be screw-mounted to a wall.\n\nThe other issue with the D5 is the inclusion of a Heltec V3 with a screen, instead of a screen less T114 (or other bfr hardware).\n\nSo, considering options here...</span> <span class=chatlog__edited-timestamp title=\"Monday, October 27, 2025 4:44 p.m.\">(edited)</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1432471119075475598", "author": "Ceres Station 🌑", "author_handle": "82a6_31995", "user_id": "1416146698115485798", "avatar": "", "timestamp": "Monday, October 27, 2025 4:48 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-27 4:48 p.m.", "text": "can you send the D5 specs/link?", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve>can you send the D5 specs/link?</span></div>", "embeds_html": [], "attachments_html": [], "reactions_html": "", "reply_html": "", "forwarded_html": ""}, {"id": "1432471689429520455", "author": "mattzz", "author_handle": "mattzz_68187", "user_id": "1410945396494172201", "avatar": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/1410945396494172201/1777162f7c90ddc7edc839991b12438b.png?size=512", "timestamp": "Monday, October 27, 2025 4:51 p.m.", "timestamp_short": "2025-10-27 4:51 p.m.", "text": "https://www.amazon.de/KEEPTEEN-Meshtastic-Repeater-Buletooth-Controller/dp/B0F1CQ5CG1", "content_html": "<div class=\"chatlog__content chatlog__markdown\"><span class=chatlog__markdown-preserve><a href=\"https://www.amazon.de/KEEPTEEN-Meshtastic-Repeater-Buletooth-Controller/dp/B0F1CQ5CG1\">https://www.amazon.de/KEEPTEEN-Meshtastic-Repeater-Buletooth-Controller/dp/B0F1CQ5CG1</a></span></div>", "embeds_html": ["<div class=chatlog__embed><div class=\"chatlog__embed-color-pill chatlog__embed-color-pill--default\"></div><div class=chatlog__embed-content-container><div class=chatlog__embed-content><div class=chatlog__embed-text><div class=chatlog__embed-title><a class=chatlog__embed-title-link href=h